modName: Outfit of the Royal High School
summary: School started to enroll students, every student can get awesome outfit, with looming underwear :-j
descriptionHtml:
- Introduction

Uniforms of the Royal High School is  a re-textures of Schoolgirl Outfit mod.
New boots + shirt ( with looming underwear ) + skirt + socks

- Installation
Just extract the file into the skyrim folder and merge it with the pre-existing data folder.

- How can i get my outfit

To any forge assuming you have the Ebony Smithing perk
or press the tilde ( ` ) button on your keyboard ( console mode ) :

player.additem (xx)a1a1a1 1
player.additem (xx)a1a1a2 1 
player.additem (xx)a1a1a3 1

(xx) is your loading order of Nexus mod manager

- Credits

Original file uploaded by person123456789
Remade into standalone version by me / imoosmoth

Thank you to all those who downloaded and endorsed. Thank you for the suggestions
